{"tid":1148112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啲回教徒又開始日出到日落期間唔飲水唔食嘢","createTime":"2019-05-10T09:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T10:08:16.000Z","uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4f85dd9354921d810bde81579bc69675c99d4afb","tid":1148112,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:10:21.000Z","msg":"而搞笑嘅係古蘭經根本無咁講<br />\n<br />\n2:185 萊麥丹月中，開始降示《古蘭經》，指導世人，昭示明證，以便遵循正道，分別真偽，故在此月中，你們應當齋戒；害病或旅行的人，當依所缺的日數補齋。真主要你們便利，不要你們困難，以便你們補足所缺的日數，以便你們讚頌真主引導你們的恩德，以便你們感謝他。"},{"pid":"25b15ceeb9bfec8b4752c25dcfa7bf3b9d70cfdd","tid":1148112,"uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/rsiczn_1X68/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Frsiczn_1X68%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=d43802f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e6335e1c1de4885db6e6fbb639cb85e2d0cac3c","tid":1148112,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25b15ceeb9bfec8b4752c25dcfa7bf3b9d70cfdd","tid":1148112,"uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/rsiczn_1X68/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Frsiczn_1X68%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=d43802f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:18:56.000Z","msg":"你係回教徒？"},{"pid":"9b3dc52b1a454f14844174e39c50253c34f6b7c1","tid":1148112,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7e6335e1c1de4885db6e6fbb639cb85e2d0cac3c","tid":1148112,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25b15ceeb9bfec8b4752c25dcfa7bf3b9d70cfdd","tid":1148112,"uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/rsiczn_1X68/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Frsiczn_1X68%2F